title: Tällihorn
text: The Tällihorn is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the Swiss <a href="Pennine%20Alps">Pennine Alps</a>, located east of the <a href="Weissmies">Weissmies</a> in the canton of <a href="Valais">Valais</a>. It lies in the <a href="Val%20Divedro">Val Divedro</a>, south of the main Alpine watershed.
